'''Mindy Kiefer''' is a fourth-year medical student who did a [[Clerkship|rotation]] at [[Grey Sloan Memorial Hospital]].


Mindy came to work as a [[Clerkship|sub-intern]] at the hospital in order to vie for a spot as a surgical intern there. On her first day, she toured the hospital and observed a surgery. ''("[[Break Down the House]]")''

After the sub-interns were challenged to find a suitable abdominal wall donor for Megan Hunt, Mindy suggested a woman had been dead for three days, making her ineligible. ''("[[Get Off on the Pain]]")''


Mindy is a fourth-year medical student doing a six-week rotation as a [[Clerkship|sub-intern]] at Grey Sloan Memorial.


*Mindy is in the top % of her medical school program.
